<item>
            <title>[LU-6123] conf-sanity test_72: FAIL: mount client failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6123</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;conf-sanity test 72 failed as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;mount lustre on /mnt/lustre.....
Starting client: shadow-52vm2.shadow.whamcloud.com:  -o user_xattr,flock shadow-52vm7@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre
CMD: shadow-52vm2.shadow.whamcloud.com mkdir -p /mnt/lustre
mkdir: cannot create directory `/mnt/lustre&apos;: File exists
CMD: shadow-52vm2.shadow.whamcloud.com mount -t lustre -o user_xattr,flock shadow-52vm7@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre
warning: /mnt/lustre: cannot resolve: Cannot send after transport endpoint shutdown
 conf-sanity test_72: @@@@@@ FAIL: mount client failed
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Console log on client:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;01:36:43:Lustre: Evicted from MGS (at 10.1.6.88@tcp) after server handle changed from 0x4724486cf472d1a2 to 0x4724486cf48d6a17
01:36:43:Lustre: MGC10.1.6.88@tcp: Connection restored to MGS (at 10.1.6.88@tcp)
01:36:43:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: mkdir -p /mnt/lustre
01:36:43:LustreError: 167-0: lustre-MDT0000-mdc-ffff88007ae1e400: This client was evicted by lustre-MDT0000; in progress operations using this service will fail.
01:36:43:LustreError: 1193:0:(file.c:3170:ll_inode_revalidate_fini()) lustre: revalidate FID [0x200000007:0x1:0x0] error: rc = -5
01:36:43:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: mount -t lustre -o user_xattr,flock shadow-52vm7@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre
01:36:43:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: /usr/sbin/lctl mark  conf-sanity test_72: @@@@@@ FAIL: mount client failed
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

